  "text": "The Civil Registration System (CRS) The CRS is a national registry of all Danish residents [CITATION_1] . A 10-digit personal identification number (PIN) is assigned to everyone at birth or immigration. The PIN was used as a linkage to the Danish HIV Cohort Study (DHCS).",
